channel.title: Eclipse-rsps V3.5 [upon request] [Added new Home Area very spread and organized]
channel.description: After my release of V3.0, i recieved about 16 Private Message's asking me if I could re-release V.3 but with a custom made home. There are really no changes from version 3, except for the new home, a new starter pack, and a couple of touchups. v.4 is on its way, im working on a new skiller island and construction :D. ~Enjoy~
